{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readAsync","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"buffer","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sv","text":"UnsafeMutableRawPointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"!, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"count","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"ioPriority"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","text":"CancellableRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil, "},{"text":"callback","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"GAsyncReadyCallback","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GAsyncReadyCallback","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil, "},{"text":"userData","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gpointer"},{"text":"? = nil)","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"During an async request no other sync and async calls are allowed on "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"stream"},{"type":"text","text":", and will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"result in ","type":"text"},{"code":"pending","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" errors."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A value of ","type":"text"},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" larger than ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"G_MAXSSIZE"},{"type":"text","text":" will cause a "},{"code":"invalidArgument","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" error.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"On success, the number of bytes read into the buffer will be passed to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"callback. It is not an error if this is not the same as the requested size, as it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"can happen e.g. near the end of a file, but generally we try to read","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"as many bytes as requested. Zero is returned on end of file","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"(or if ","type":"text"},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is zero),  but never otherwise.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Any outstanding i\/o request with higher priority (lower numerical value) will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be executed before an outstanding request with lower priority. Default"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"priority is [PRIORITY_DEFAULT](\/\/documentation\/glib\/priority_default.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The asynchronous methods have a default fallback that uses threads to implement","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"asynchronicity, so they are optional for inheriting classes. However, if you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"override one you must override all."}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/InputStream","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/InputStream\/InputStreamProtocol-Implementations"]]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Request an asynchronous read of "},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" bytes from 